Here's Jesse, the start of a new scenario editor that is being built
by me.

Everything that doesn't work is disabled right now.  Yes, it works for
Windows and nothing else.  When (definitely not if) I get everything
operational, I'll translate it into C/C++.

Everything you see in the menus is planned functionality and yes, the
program size will keep growing bigger.  I'll have to stop to add some
documentation before I can do some more functionality to it.

* * *

I sent an email to you guys at Sourceforge, and I would like a
response back whenever you guys get a chance.
